text: Student Tour is a 1934 American musical movie directed by Charles Reisner and starring Jimmy Durante, Charles Butterworth, Maxine Doyle, Phil Regan, Douglas Fowley, Nelson Eddy. It was distributed by Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer. == Other websites == * Category:1934 musical movies Category:American musical movies Category:MGM movies Category:Movies directed by Charles Reisner
